{"tid":91924,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"墨西哥度假勝地 發現12具屍體","createTime":"2017-01-23T07:47:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-23T07:56:13.000Z","uid":61888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"001726480942f49fbcb00d8c15540566fb68e747","tid":91924,"uid":61888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T07:47:07.000Z","msg":"法新社墨西哥瓜達拉哈拉22日電） 週末在墨西哥西部濱周度假勝地曼札尼約（Manzanillo）發現12具屍體，顯然是毒品暴力下的受害者。 事發地點是廣受美國和各國遊客歡迎的度假勝地， 發生這樣的駭聞令人吃驚。在此之前，這個區域與墨西 哥其他區域不同，鮮少傳出血腥毒品暴力事件。 7人昨天陳屍在1輛被棄在曼札尼約路邊的計程車上 。"},{"pid":"45e46dd89fff0e2c4c4495f5e06aed7cfb28b36f","tid":91924,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T07:50:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9edb408ec0d0f3d29d75e0d4c772df1d7b264f6a","tid":91924,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T07:51:13.000Z","msg":"濱周渡假勝地"},{"pid":"ca90b9e94409212601863b9e4b1f2ea094b2768d","tid":91924,"uid":54929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T07:56:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}